original: Kjelliman, Per Joihan, ilandskiamrerare, HaIm!Sta’d, f. 26/11/92 i HaDmsitad av här :skriv. Oscar K. o. Agnes Dahlberg. G. 20 m. Ella Karin Ljungberg. Barn: Folke f. 26, Lars 39. — Stud:-ex. 10, jur. kand. 16. Landskont. i HaLl. I. 18, länsbokhåll. av 1. gr. 19, llänsasse’sisor 30, taxiintemd. 44, l’and’s.-fcamir. 47. Ordf. i tax :nd m. m. Hoibby: fisike. RVO.
translated: Kjelliman, Per Joihan, land clerk, HaIm!Sta’d, b. 26/11/92 in HaDmsitad, parents: Oscar K. and Agnes Dahlberg. Married on the 20th with Ella Karin Ljungberg. Children: Folke b. 26, Lars b. 39. Completed high school exams in 1910, graduated with a law degree in 1916. Worked as a county clerk in HaLl. I. from 1918, senior county accountant from 1919, county assessor from 1930, taxi operator since 1944, and land tax officer from 1947. Also served as chairman of the taxi association. Hobbies: fishing. Awarded the Royal Order of Vasa.
